{
  "stem": "23774.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had to go into the police and register themself-- their name, age, address.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And whatever they have on them, the police took it away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they put up in groups of 60 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they took them away to a forest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a village called Kozak, K-O-Z-A-K.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there were pits dug, two big ones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And as they took them there in groups of 60s to the pits, there were a few Ukrainian police.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were a few Gestapo ones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that day, Shavuot, they killed-- shot in cold blood-- 2,200 people. 1,600 women and children and 600 men.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now, before they came to the pit, about 500 meters, they stopped.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They undressed them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They took all the clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the people went naked to the pit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when they came there, they shot them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they were killing up to 4 o'clock in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "If they brought you from the city after 4:00, you survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They wouldn't kill you anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So they killed at that time 2,200 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Women and children were 16-- [VOICE BREAKS] [SOBBING] [SNIFFLING] [CLEARS THROAT] And then-- and then the rest of these survived.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They came back to the city, and the Gestapo and the police said, from now on, you can move over on one street.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And you can start going back to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And there would be no more killings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was at home with my family-- my mother, my sister, and my brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had in our home-- we had a basement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we made a other basement under that basement that in case anything, we run in, and we hide there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that's where we-- the day of Shavuot-- we were hiding.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
